   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-a" mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>Have you been to her grave?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-b" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>I'll take revenge on your behalf</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-c" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>That face doesn't do anything for you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-d" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>That's why you look so sad.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>You can remember what I told you last time. Yes, it's the anniversary today. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Deckard looks so sad)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>I've just been there. The grasses are growing all over now. I haven't taken care of it for a long time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>Thank you for saying that but I want to avenge my wife by myself. Plus, the monster is not an ordinary one. You're not ready to hear that story yet.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>I know this is not like me. But sometimes facial muscles betray their owner.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>On the anniversary, I was reminded of what happened that day. When my wife was killed, I realized that the world didn't change at all even though she had died. I felt very sad because one's death seemed so insignificant, just like dust in the world. Haha! Don't look at me with those sad eyes of yours.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
